    "The Lagrangian vertices are thenL v = √ -g λ v   (g µν) pv (ε µνρσ) qv (n µ) kv (∇ ν) lv f ∈L Φ f µ 1 •••µ S f (η, x) N v,f   contract = λ v a 4-lv (η)   (η µν) pv (ϵ µνρσ) qv (n µ) kv (∂ ν) lv f ∈L Φf µ 1 •••µ S f (η, x) N v,f   contract +O(∂ lv-1) ≡ λ v D v ΦNv +O(∂ lv-1).",
    "(4.14)Here, ε µνρσ = √ -gϵ µνρσ is the covariant Levi-Civita tensor density.",
